jiuxian.com/images/upload/Image/1(114).jpg\" /> </dl><!--detail_prtpic over--></div>\r\n<!--part_box over-->\r\n<div class=\"part_box clearfix\" sizset=\"38\" sizcache=\"39\">\r\n<h4 class=\"h4_ass\" sizset=\"38\" sizcache=\"39\">品牌文化</h4>\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"780\" sizset=\"41\" sizcache=\"17\">\r\n    <tbody sizset=\"41\" sizcache=\"17\">\r\n        <tr sizset=\"41\" sizcache=\"17\">\r\n            <td sizset=\"41\" sizcache=\"17\"><img src=\"http://img01.jiuxian.com/upload/goods/1099/b/1362640731412.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></td>\r\n            <td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td><font color=\"#666666\" size=\"2\">舍得酒之所以被誉为&ldquo;酒中新贵&rdquo;，除了因为它酿千古文化于一壶的非凡底蕴，还因为其行业领先的&ldquo;生态酿酒&rdquo;技术所带来的独特复合优雅香型口感。舍得酒的生态酿酒园正坐落在这一酒中福地。在这个绿意盎然的生态园里，处处生机勃勃，溢满了生命的气息。尤其非同寻常的是，园内种满了银杏树，这种素有&ldquo;活化石&rdquo;之称的神奇树木，奇迹般地调节着这里的空气成分，造就了几乎是世界上最适合酿酒的小生态圈。不但酿酒生态园高人一筹，舍得酒的生态酿酒技术更是领先一步。舍得酒运用了国际领先的生物技术，利用活的生态菌酿酒，在酒里注入了奇妙的&ldquo;生气&rdquo;，这样酿出来的酒，不但鲜香动人，更神奇般地散发着只有几十年的陈酒才具有的浓香和醇味。 </font></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--part_box over-->\r\n<div class=\"part_box clearfix\" sizset=\"39\" sizcache=\"39\">\r\n<h4 class=\"h4_ass\" sizset=\"39\" sizcache=\"39\">酒厂介绍</h4>\r\n<p sizset=\"42\" sizcache=\"17\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"780\" sizset=\"42\" sizcache=\"17\">\r\n    <tbody sizset=\"42\" sizcache=\"17\">\r\n        <tr sizset=\"42\" sizcache=\"17\">\r\n            <td sizset=\"42\" sizcache=\"17\">\r\n            <p sizset=\"42\" sizcache=\"17\"><img src=\"http://img01.jiuxian.com/upload/goods/4289/m/1352272129507.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n            <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <p><font color=\"#333333\" size=\"2\"><strong>四川沱牌曲酒股份有限公司</strong></font></p>\r\n            <p><font col