p align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" sizset=\"41\" sizcache=\"17\"><img src=\"http://img01.jiuxian.com/upload/goods/13451/g/1387338432172.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" sizset=\"42\" sizcache=\"17\"><img src=\"http://img01.jiuxian.com/upload/goods/13451/g/1387338439157.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n</dl><!--detail_prtpic over--></div>\r\n<!--part_box over-->\r\n<div class=\"part_box clearfix\" sizset=\"37\" sizcache=\"39\">\r\n<h4 class=\"h4_ass\" sizset=\"37\" sizcache=\"39\">品牌文化</h4>\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"780\" sizset=\"43\" sizcache=\"17\">\r\n    <tbody sizset=\"43\" sizcache=\"17\">\r\n        <tr sizset=\"43\" sizcache=\"17\">\r\n            <td sizset=\"43\" sizcache=\"17\"><img src=\"http://img01.jiuxian.com/upload/goods/9425/b/1382433686364.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></td>\r\n            <td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td><font color=\"#666666\" size=\"2\">1367年，一无名氏遵循史载，按图所骥，在&ldquo;锦江春&rdquo;原址开设&ldquo;富春烧坊&rdquo;，所产&ldquo;锦江春&rdquo;窖香浓郁，绵醇甘冽，一时之间声名鹊起，为成都首推美酒。明末清初，一名颇有胆识的客商吸收当时成都各酒家的传统工艺，于乾隆五十一年（公元1786年）选中了&ldquo;富春烧坊&rdquo;原址，即现在的水井街开创 &ldquo;福升全&rdquo;，&ldquo;福升全&rdquo;的酿酒师选用&ldquo;薛涛井&rdquo;水创造新酿，&ldquo;薛涛酒&rdquo;刚一问世，即大获成功。顿时间，&ldquo;福升全&rdquo;烧坊门庭若市，供不应求。</font></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"780\" sizset=\"44\" sizcache=\"17\">\r\n    <tbody sizset=\"44\" sizcache=\"17\">\r\n        <tr sizset=\"44\" sizcache=\"17\">\r\n            <td sizset=\"44\" sizcache=\"17\"><img src=\"http://img01.jiuxian.com/upload/goods/9425/b/1382434106417.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></td>\r\n            <td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td><font color=\"#666666\" size=\"2\">1824年，&ldquo;福升全&rdquo;烧坊已门庭若市，供不应求，所以另择新址暑袜街，建号&ldquo;全兴成&rdquo;，生产&ldquo;全兴酒&rdquo;。烧坊古色古香，门额上黑底金字匾额：全兴成。 大门两边则是清代著名学者梁章钜的对联：&ldquo;入座三杯醉者也，出门一拱歪之乎。&rdquo;&mdash;&mdash;&ldquo;全兴成&rdquo;楹联。</font></td>\r\n        </tr